<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150888>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Bulbophyllum annamense. A. Flowering plant. B. Leaf apex, adaxial side. C. Inflorescence with peduncle. D. Inflorescence. E. Flower, half-side view. F. Flower, with lateral sepals removed, side view. G. Dorsal sepal, abaxial and adaxial side. H & I. Apex of median sepal. J. Lateral sepals, adaxial and abaxial side. K. Petals, abaxial and adaxial side. L. Lip, views from different sides. M. Pedicel, ovary, and column, side view. N. Ovary and column, side view. O. Column apex. P. Anther cap, view from above and from below. Q. Pollinaria.All photo by Truong Ba Vuong from specimen BV 628, photo correction and design by L. Averyanov and T. Maisak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

